<div class="heading resPageHeading">


























<h1 >Making robots, creating companions</h1></div>

<div class="content stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resImageText section">


























		<div class="row" id="8f68c243-d755-421b-8d42-7f4ef4087c86">
			<div class="col-xs-12">
				<div class="thumbnail customStyle1">
					
<img src="/content/dam/research/images/newsletter/2020-07/designing-robot-companions-0.jpg" alt="Four 3D renderings of robots lined up, including three humanoids and one dog"/>




					 
						<div class="caption richtextContent empty">
	
